## Machine Learning Components

- **Placement:** **All inference on host PC** for now; **Quest 3 displays** outputs only (`docs/FinalStretchDoc.md`).
- **Facial expression:** Third-party **[MorphCast](https://www.morphcast.com/)** with Quest 3 cameras; **tabular outputs** feed feature builders on the PC (not assumed: in-house CNN on raw video).
- **Fast path:** **Random Forest** on multimodal tabular features → **discrete labels** for frequent updates (`docs/MLOptions.md`).
- **Interval path:** Second model on **time windows** (length TBD, e.g. ~5–30 s); richer situational summaries; **start simple** (tabular / tree-based on aggregated features); exact algorithm **TBD** with data.
- **Future (optional):** Continuous arousal/stress-style scores—parked until needed.
- **Out of scope:** Voice / microphone emotion—do not plan as active work.

